title: Ham Taylor - Lost in Time!
description:
Ham Taylor: Lost in Time is the first step in an incredible journey spanning space, time, and everything in between.

When an unstoppable comet sets its sights on New York City - the time machine, and its creator, are the only hope humanity has left.

From the near future to a long forgotten past, falling skyscrapers to rising pyramids, Ham Taylor is put to the ultimate test in this battle to save the world.

Your adventure starts here!
